 :$\paren {S_1 \subseteq T} \land \paren {S_2 \subseteq T} \implies \paren {S_1 \cup S_2} \subseteq T$\n{{qed|lemma}}\n=== Sufficient Condition ===\nLet $\paren {S_1 \cup S_2} \subseteq T$: 
