 | c = [[Definition:Associative Operation|Associativity of $\circ'$]] 
 }}\n{{eqn | r = x \circ' \left({z \circ' y^{-1} }\right) \circ' w^{-1} 
 | c = [[Commutation with Inverse in Monoid]] 
 }}\n{{eqn | r = \left({x \circ' z}\right) \circ' \left({y^{-1} \circ' w^{-1} }\right) 
