=== Inverse Completion is a Field ===
We have that: 
 :the [[Definition:Algebraic Structure|algebraic structure]] $\struct {K, +}$ is an [[Definition:Abelian Group|abelian group]] 
 :the [[Definition:Algebraic Structure|algebraic structure]] $\struct {K^*, \circ}$ is an [[Definition:Abelian Group|abelian group]] 
 :the operation $\circ$ [[Definition:Distributive Operation|distributes]] over $+$.
