We also have that $\struct {K, +, \circ}$ [[Definition:Submagma|contains $\struct {D, +, \circ}$ algebraically]] such that: 
 :$ orall x \in K: \exists z \in D, y \in D^*: z = \dfrac x y$
Thus $\struct {K, +, \circ}$ is a [[Definition:Field of Quotients|field of quotients]] of $\struct {D, +, \circ}$. 
